summary: i am not really in the phandom anymore but hell even i miss dan. he was a big part of my teenage to young adult years like six...
body: i am not really in the phandom anymore but hell even i miss dan. he was a big part of my teenage to young adult years like six to seven years back when i was a clueless young adult so yknow a part of me will always respect and love him. and he has been absent from twitter for almost a month now he’s like literally gone off the world. few years back i had a thought that youtube are not forever, some time in the future all these youtubers that i love might get sick of yt or they might want to do something else and i was thinking how would they go about distancing themselves from yt. maybe this is how idek anymore. i hope this hiatus that dan is taking is going to be great for his health, mentally and physically, and when he is ready he will come back happy and healthy. and if he decide not to come back, be happy dan! really, be happy be healthy i still love you 7 years later and i will love you forever.
